Sections 11-52-3, 11-52-14, and 11-52-15, Code of Alabama
HB468 INTRODUCED
29 1975, to remove the prohibition against a local official
30 serving on a municipal planning commission; and to amend
31 Section 11-88-6, Code of Alabama 1975, to remove the
32 prohibition against a municipal official from serving on the
33 board of directors of a local water, sewer, or fire protection
34 authority.
35 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF ALABAMA:
