230 b. The the first term of another director shall begin
231 immediately upon his or her election and shall end at noon on
232 March 1 of the second succeeding odd-numbered calendar year
233 following the election; and.
234 c. The the first term of the remaining director shall
235 begin immediately upon his or her election and shall end at
236 noon on March 1 of the third succeeding odd-numbered calendar
237 year following the election.
238 (2) Thereafter, the term of office of each director
239 shall be six years.
